high_descs: Turn left and go to the sink
Grab a large knife out of the sink
Turn right and stop at the counter
Cut the lettuce on the counter into slices
Moves slightly to the left
Put the knife on the counter
Move slightly to the right
Grab a slice of the lettuce
Turn left and go to the sink
Wash the lettuce in the sink and then take it out
Turn around and go to the table
Put the lettuce slice on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a clean slice of lettuce on the table

high_descs: Turn around, step forward, then turn right and go to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the knife with the yellow blade in the center of the sink.
Turn right, step forward, then turn left at the kitchen counter.
Slice the cabbage to the left of the ladle.
Turn left, step forward, then turn right to face the counter.
Stand the knife up on the counter to the right of the sink.
Return to the sliced cabbage.
Pick up the center slice of cabbage
Turn left and walk to the left edge of the sink.
Place the cabbage slice in the sink in front of the knife, turn on the water for a few seconds then turn off and pick up the cabbage.
Turn around, step forward, then turn right and walk to the kitchen table on the right.
Place the cabbage upright on the handle of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Wash a slice of cabbage and place on the spoon.

high_descs: Turn left and face the sink in front of you.
Take the knife from the sink in front of you.
Turn right and face the counter with the lettuce on your left.
Slice the lettuce in front of you.
Turn left and face the sink on your right.
Place the knife on the counter by the sink in front of you.
Turn right and face the lettuce on your left.
Take a lettuce slice off of the counter in front of you.
Turn left and face the sink on your right.
Place the lettuce in the sink in front of you, wash it, and take it out.
Turn around and face the table to your right.
Place the lettuce slice on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean lettuce slice on the table.
